Headline: Alex Gonzaga reacts to pregnancy rumor – Manila Bulletin
Text: Popular vlogger-celebrity endorser Alex Gonzaga has reacted to rumors that she was having a baby.“Wooops. Sorry hindi pa po. Ibang blessing po sinasabi ko. Waking up every morning is a already a blessing,” said Gonzaga following rumors that she and husband Mikee Morada are already expecting.The “new blessing” tweet of Alex has sparked a pregnancy rumor.READ MORE: https://mb.com.ph/2021/03/24/netizens-ask-is-alex-gonzaga-pregnant/Still some fans have expressed support to Alex.“Parang buntis kana talaga maam Alex, kasi tumaba mukha mo.. But congrats po sa inyo,” an online user wrote.Another wrote: “Sis alam mo di ako nakatulog kakaisip tas di pala yun yon. naka ready na dress ko para maging ninang ano ba @Mscathygonzaga.”“Grabe buong gabi ako nag- isip at kinabahan dun.”
